},{"pid":"af3dd1a9872b771525f09f8a404b70a805df80b2","tid":455842,"uid":74013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T12:55:00.000Z","msg":"出現幻覺?"},{"pid":"347e878255e5126a730d2aea3a56532bc9a48f76","tid":455842,"uid":140802,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T12:55:25.000Z","msg":"小建議 <br />\n太長 要睇晒同理解晒 再分析有d難度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可能我太蠢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"686b8959c9ed7299332e2cd50ab2b099720197c0","tid":455842,"uid":43046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T12:55:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>出現幻覺?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nNO"},{"pid":"400f73795d9a2bc5bcb6307b514535902d596e0b","tid":455842,"uid":11312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T12:55:38.000Z","msg":"森林嘅一天係出面世界嘅更長時間（一年，十年）？"},{"pid":"59b52061a42f4cd334e9c9a9523f6289fc94325e","tid":455842,"uid":131980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T12:55:41.000Z","msg":"肉係人肉"},{"pid":"e66890502c3b5749d21db8e759e1f4e077209183","tid":455842,"uid":77318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T12:58:03.000Z","msg":"最後壯漢食左自己 ?<br />\n叫埋馬田食"},{"pid":"ba8e04bbe930b442440ee838e8b7ad1297e2e474","tid":455842,"uid":43046,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T12:58:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>森林嘅一天係出面世界嘅更長時間（一年，十年）？</blockquote><br />\n部分YES"},{"pid":"c5ab103f81fec59971a4f37c9efcdb364ea6214c","tid":455842,"uid":140802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T12:58:36.000Z","msg":"馬田贏左之後想叫自己唔好參加<br />\n返去以前世界救自己？"},{"pid":"ae94e579131879a91d8e3af18fd36b87d1d91094","tid":455842,"uid":43046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T12:58:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>肉係人肉</blockquote><br />\nYES"},{"pid":"150e8d358b563e297101f4035a09e4dad909dd26","tid":455842,"uid":43046,"like":0,